entry.programlisting:
In <summary> tags, use ```  above and below each code block.
In <remarks> tags, do not use ```. Ensure all other text runs on from the start and each line ends with <!--newline>\.

The last line before the code block will typically be:
/// __Example__:<!–newline-->\
///

Then add the code, starting on the next comment line:
{
    "id": "string"

}

